title: Will the Pixel 5 launch in India?
content: Avid Pixel user, couldn't upgrade to Pixel 4 since it didn't launch in India - but I'm not sure why the Pixel 5 isn't coming here since it doesn't have the soli chip (which prevented the 4 from launching)? I genuinely do not want to switch to a different brand, and going for the 4a will be a downgrade..
